# 802.3 + LLC/SNAP encapsulating IPv4. LLC DSAP/SSAP 0xAA + control 0x03, SNAP OUI 0x000000 +
# EtherType 0x0800, so SNAP routes to IPv4 through the shared ethertype demux (SNAP is a drop-in
# ethertype parent). source: constructed spec-accurate frame; tshark dissects eth:llc:snap:ip.
